\paragraphHdNospace{Conditional clause.}
Sometimes users hypothesize about their health conditions, such as ``If I lost my appetite for days at a time, that... wouldn't be sustainable for me.''.
We remove these posts by using regular expressions to identify popular conditional clause formats.